## 4. Typography Composites

The system uses composite tokens to bundle font properties (Family, Weight, Size, Line Height).

| Composite Token | Composition |
|-----------------|-------------|
| `text-5xl/font-semibold` | `font-size/8` (48px) + `font-weight/semibold` (600) + `line-height/8` (64px) |
| `text-2xl/font-medium` | `font-size/5` (24px) + `font-weight/medium` (500) + `line-height/5` (32px) |
| `text-xl/font-medium` | `font-size/4` (20px) + `font-weight/medium` (500) + `line-height/4` (27px) |
| `text-base/font-medium` | `font-size/2` (16px) + `font-weight/medium` (500) + `line-height/2` (21px) |

